  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK462">
<l>terinta viṉattōṭu tērnteṇṇic ceyvārk</l>
<l> karumporuḷ yātoṉṟu mil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is nothing too difficult to (be attained by) those who, before they act, reflect well themselves, and thoroughly consider (the matter) with chosen friends.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
